title: Breathing Fire - Live in Jamaica [Mp3 VBR V0]
description:
Live album recorded in 1988 at Fort Charles, Jamaica. Starring Jimmy Cliff, Ziggy Marley, Bunny Wailer, Rita Marley and the I-Threes (Sly Dunbar, Robbie Shakespeare and Toots Hibbert), are joined by Carlos Santana, Chrissie Hynde, Grace Jones and The Neville Brothers for a once in a lifetime celebration of that unique sound that combines Jamaican folk music and Afro-Caribbean dance rhythms into the music they call reggae.
